"display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: 0.5em;height: 0.5em;border-radius: 50%;background-color: rgb(225, 54, 89);box-sizing: border-box;\"></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br  /></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;\">十多年前，电商的兴起大大打击了实体店的生意，消费者从线下向线上转移，看着以往门庭若市的店面渐渐变得寥寥无几，商家也做出了很多努力，发传单，猛打折，送礼品，然而许多时候收效甚微。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br  /></span></p></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img data-ratio=\"0.6666667\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/w9GMnwKCInXrjZZFA3aPvlOWGIGerRChJEr7PibJeTpG4hcFZO8XTjJyMu0zB4CwgayG43Suw5iavPK9Thx9B3Ag/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"450\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;\"  /></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.5;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"  /></p></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.5;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box;letter-spacing: 1px;\">纵观这几年的发展情况，产能过剩、全球化、人均收入提高、消费者心理诉求变化才是导致实体店不好做的真正原因。可这些是时代趋势，无可避免。</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"  /></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"  /></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">难道，实体经济真的无处缝生了吗？</span></p></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 40%;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img data-ratio=\"1.1\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/w9GMnwKCInXrjZZFA3aPvlOWGIGerRChCwT3iamKsPNzSRNibiaruicLhKWSSQeUx7hhASWHAREfrMUZeQsrgsvSBg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"60\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" width=\"100%\"  /></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.5;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以往消费者都是在\"体验\"这一点上觉得实体店要比网络购物更有优势。尽管目前各个渠道的购物体验都在不断的改善，但在体验性这一点而言，实体店确实拥有着绝对的优势。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"  /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而作为优势，许多实体店并不重视！！！</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br  /></span></p></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 50%;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img data-ratio=\"1.0171875\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/w9GMnwKCInXrjZZFA3aPvlOWGIGerRChg2BUWQlPGEgLHM3iaJIYDib9icM5Uc7AjGxXIJsXnkgvKxZ1cWEhNp3pg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" width=\"100%\"  /></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.5;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"  /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现在消费者对实体店的印象是什么？坑！态度差！服务质量堪忧！</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"  /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以下是网友分享的经历：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br  /></span></p></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;overflow: hidden !important;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img data-ratio=\"0.3265625\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/w9GMnwKCInXrjZZFA3aPvlOWGIGerRChRG2ibOibRVhGdDfPNkRuicgwnvtsibufsiaHK9mGgKuKbC3micjOQ3hUVYtQ/64